column16: Jake Goebbert flies out to left fielder Ender Inciarte.
Alexi Amarista singles on a line drive to right fielder Cody Ross.   Rene Rivera scores.
Umpire reviewed (home run), call on the field was upheld: Rene Rivera triples (1) on a fly ball to center fielder A.  J.   Pollock.
Dee Gordon singles on a ground ball to center fielder Ender Inciarte.   Roger Bernadina scores.    Justin Turner to 3rd.
Andre Ethier flies out to right fielder Cody Ross.
Justin Turner reaches on a fielder's choice, fielded by third baseman Aaron Hill.   Roger Bernadina to 2nd.
Joc Pederson flies out to left fielder Nolan Reimold.
Juan Uribe singles on a ground ball to shortstop Cliff Pennington.
Alexi Amarista grounds out, second baseman Chris Owings to first baseman Mark Trumbo.
Yangervis Solarte lines out to left fielder Alfredo Marte.
Abraham Almonte grounds out, shortstop Didi Gregorius to first baseman Mark Trumbo.
